303
00:22:41,458 --> 00:22:43,125
Hello, Chibiko.

304
00:22:43,208 --> 00:22:45,208
Silvia?

305
00:22:45,291 --> 00:22:48,000
How do you know me?

306
00:22:48,500 --> 00:22:50,750
I saw Apollo in a dream...

307
00:22:50,833 --> 00:22:53,583
